<title>HONG KONG: Fu Hui 1996 net loss HK$124.16 mln.</title>
<headline>Fu Hui 1996 net loss HK$124.16 mln.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-04-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended December 31</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	 32.41 loss  vs 11.96 loss</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)  nil	   vs nil</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	82.60 loss  vs 28.90 loss</p>
<p>    Net			  124.16 loss vs 45.82 loss</p>
<p>    Turnover		   500.70	vs 180.59</p>
<p>    Company name	     Fu Hui Jewellery Co (H.K.) Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		N/A</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	 N/A</p>
<p>NOTE - Fu Hui makes jewellery for overseas markets.</p>
<p>Net is after an exceptional loss of HK$99.77 million on provision for slow-moving inventories, gain of HK$15.26 million on disposal of land and building, and gain of HK$1.91 million on disposal of an associated company.</p>
<p>Total dividend for year is nil vs nil.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6368</p>
